go through, with all sorts of

00:09:38.950 --> 00:09:40.680
different side things
going on.

00:09:40.680 --> 00:09:43.260
So this is a really, really
full category.

00:09:43.260 --> 00:09:44.580
But this game is very good.

00:09:44.580 --> 00:09:48.640
