compatibility stuff thrown in.

00:10:16.050 --> 00:10:17.900
So there's a couple of things
I like in the change.

00:10:17.900 --> 00:10:19.550
I'd also like to make sure
that they're actually

00:10:19.550 --> 00:10:22.010
correctly targeting
the screen.

00:10:22.010 --> 00:10:22.700
IAN NI-LEWIS: Great stuff.

00:10:22.700 --> 00:10:25.500
So let's go ahead and talk
about Metro Rush.

