00:11:48.570 --> 00:11:50.020
IAN NI-LEWIS: So it's
a little buggy.

00:11:50.020 --> 00:11:54.010
And let's face it, this mechanic
has been done before,

00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:55.340
it's been done better.

00:11:55.340 --> 00:11:57.110
Witness--

00:11:57.110 --> 00:11:58.420
I call up the--

00:11:58.420 --> 00:12:00.380
DAN GALPIN: My favorite thing
is this at the bottom.

00:12:00.380 --> 00:12:02.680
Like, the five guys that are
all like standing to hop on

00:12:02.680 --> 00:12:03.610
each other at the bottom
of the screen.

00:12:03.610 --> 00:12:04.920
But yes, it it is
a little buggy.

00:12:04.920 --> 00:12:06.380
IAN NI-LEWIS: Yeah, you remember
that bathroom game

00:12:06.380 --> 00:12:09.080
where they had first
men, women.

