someone on YouTube.

00:14:12.210 --> 00:14:12.820
DAN GALPIN: Oh.

00:14:12.820 --> 00:14:13.780
Important.

00:14:13.780 --> 00:14:17.440
DAN PHAM: The question is, how
can you play with beer?

