This a game that we actually
were unable to get to run on

00:16:24.553 --> 00:16:24.910
any of our devices.

00:16:24.910 --> 00:16:25.950
IAN NI-LEWIS: I can't even tell
you how much I wanted to

00:16:25.950 --> 00:16:26.470
play this game.

00:16:26.470 --> 00:16:28.360
DAN GALPIN: Yeah,
we were excited.

