00:17:34.430 --> 00:17:35.750
IAN NI-LEWIS: So what
class was it?

00:17:35.750 --> 00:17:39.300
DAN GALPIN: Unfortunately, when
you have a class that is

00:17:39.300 --> 00:17:42.820
from the main activity class, it
prevents the main activity

00:17:42.820 --> 00:17:46.200
class from loading, but you
can't see what it is.

00:17:46.200 --> 00:17:48.390
Because you just see, oh,
the main activity

00:17:48.390 --> 00:17:49.290
class failed to load.

00:17:49.290 --> 00:17:52.990
Because one of the things it's
