00:17:58.540 --> 00:18:01.560
DAN GALPIN: It depends
on where it crashes,

00:18:01.560 --> 00:18:02.270
unfortunately.

00:18:02.270 --> 00:18:03.890
IAN NI-LEWIS: Did
you strace it?

00:18:03.890 --> 00:18:06.310
DAN GALPIN: I did
not strace it.

