Because you're tilting the
device all over the place.

00:30:25.670 --> 00:30:28.020
Do you see how hard I'm trying
not to say the F-word now?

00:30:28.020 --> 00:30:32.030
DAN GALPIN: Well, on a tablet,
this game kind of sucks

00:30:32.030 --> 00:30:33.220
because of that.

00:30:33.220 --> 00:30:37.300
IAN NI-LEWIS: It's one thing
when you have a mechanic where

00:30:37.300 --> 00:30:39.310
there's a couple buttons on the
side of the screen that

00:30:39.310 --> 00:30:40.560
