to be frustrating for

00:30:50.680 --> 00:30:53.880
most of your users, no matter
what kind of device they have.

00:30:53.880 --> 00:30:54.210
DAN GALPIN: Yeah.

00:30:54.210 --> 00:30:57.000
And the other thing is, in
general, accelerometer games

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:59.680
on tablets have to
be really, really

00:30:59.680 --> 00:31:01.350
