you can plug them right in.

00:58:12.680 --> 00:58:15.450
PerfHUD works that way, Adreno
Profiler works that way.

00:58:15.450 --> 00:58:18.450
PVRTune is slowly
getting there.

00:58:18.450 --> 00:58:22.750
I mean, the thing with PVR is
that you'll run into weird,

00:58:22.750 --> 00:58:25.670
goofy performance bugs with
PVR-- like, things that you

00:58:25.670 --> 00:58:28.520
