optimizations, you may be

00:58:44.040 --> 00:58:47.120
shocked that one little
operation you do causes things

00:58:47.120 --> 00:58:49.470
to suddenly slow down by
orders of magnitude.

00:58:49.470 --> 00:58:50.500
